# Add Custom Slots to a Lex Chatbot

- ✔️ Set up a new chatbot from scratch on Amazon Lex
- ✔️ Train your bot to recognise greetings and respond like a pro
- ✔️ Add custom error handling when your bot gets confused
- ✔️ Create custom slots so your bot can collect specific user info
- ✔️ Test your chatbot in real-time
- ✔️ Delete your AWS resources properly (so you don’t get surprise bills!)

Chatbots use several AI technologies to create natural-feeling conversation with users:
- NLP to understand what you're asking.
- Generative AI to create helpful answers.
- Speech recognition to capture input given through speech.

